		<content type="html" xml:base="/index.php/desktopdev/mstech/msaccess/accessvbajetsql/why-you-should-not-add/#comment-5937"><![CDATA[<p>Many years ago when I used to teach Access, the courses that I was required to follow included how to use Table design formatting.  So I taught the students how to do it, but stressed that it should never be done and that all formatting should be in Forms and Reports.</p>
